      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah, exactly. it's like the feeling of finally being able to just... exit. no more reservations to make, no more tickets to buy. just a final, quiet stop where you don't have to keep moving anymore. does that make sense? like, the whole point of a trip is to eventually come home and rest.",
